ithin 5-7 business days after we receive the returned item. The amount is credited back to your original payment method. For COD orders, refunds are transferred to your bank account."},{q:"How can I track my order?",a:"Once your order is shipped, you'll receive an SMS and email with the tracking link. You can also check the status anytime from the 'My Orders' section on our website."},{q:"What payment methods are accepted?",a:"We accept Cash on Delivery (COD), Credit/Debit Cards (Visa, Mastercard, RuPay), UPI (Google Pay, PhonePe, Paytm), Net Banking, and EMI options on select cards."},{q:"Do you ship across India?",a:"Yes, we deliver to all serviceable pin codes across India, including tier-2 and tier-3 cities. Free delivery on orders above ₹2,000."},{q:"How do I choose the right size?",a:"We recommend referring to our size chart on each product page. If you're between sizes, we suggest going with the larger size. You can also exchange for a different size within 7 days."}],x4=()=>p.jsxs("div",{className:"container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-3xl",children:[p.jsx("h1",{className:"font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8 text-center",children:"FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS"}),p.jsx(y4,{type:"single",collapsible:!0,className:"space-y-2",children:v4.map((e,t)=>p.jsxs(zb,{value:`faq-${t}`,className:"bg-card border border-border rounded-lg px-6",children:[p.jsx($b,{className:"text-sm font-semibold text-left hover:no-underline",children:e.q}),p.jsx(Bb,{className:"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed",children:e.a})]},t))})]}),w4=()=>{const[e,t]=w.useState(!0),[n,r]=w.useState(""),[s,o]=w.useState(""),i=a=>{a.preventDefault(),e?Vr.success("Welcome back to Foot Rush!"):Vr.success("Account created! Welcome to Foot Rush!")};return p.jsx("div",{className:"min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center px-4",children:p.jsxs("div",{className:"w-full max-w-md",children:[p.jsxs("div",{className:"text-center mb-8",children:[p.jsx("h1",{className:"font-display text-4xl mb-2",childre